
The "Local" part of the layout is everything below the context banner
and above the footer.

It should have one of the following structures:

option 1: with left column
------------------------------

#local
  #column_left
    %nav#local_nav
  #column_center.with_left
    %article#content

option 2: with right column
-----------------------------

#local
  #column_center.with_right
    %article#content
  #column_right
    %nav#local_nav

option 2: full width
-------------------------------

#local
  #column_center.full
    %article#content

